name: Ugoe Template
body:
### LaTeX template for Georg-August-Universität Göttingen talks
This is a simple and clean, inofficial LaTeX template that can be used by students.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out the documentation at https://help.github.com/pages or contact support@github.com and we’ll help you sort it out.
